associate these traits with positive things or negative

00:12:40.870 --> 00:12:43.130
things. And so, if I personally thought to

00:12:43.130 --> 00:12:45.760
myself, oh, that person has all these identifiers,

00:12:45.760 --> 00:12:52.210
they have lighter skin, pigmentation. They have hair

00:12:52.210 --> 00:12:57.330
that's a little bit straighter then I think to myself, oh they must be from the

00:12:57.330 --> 00:13:00.650
North Eastern part of Kenya because they, they

00:13:00.650 --> 00:13:02.680
have Somali blood in them or something like that.

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:03.648
&gt;&gt; Mm-hm.

00:13:03.648 --> 00:13:06.190
&gt;&gt; And then, then from there after,

00:13:06.190 --> 00:13:08.790
having identified them with a certain tribe

00:13:08.790 --> 00:13:12.450
or a certain group of people then, personally what do I think of those people.

00:13:12.450 --> 00:13:12.901
&gt;&gt; Mm-hm.

00:13:12.901 --> 00:13:14.560
&gt;&gt; And so if I thought to myself, oh I love

00:13:14.560 --> 00:13:17.120
Somali people, then I would try and make friends with that person.

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:17.582
&gt;&gt; Mm-hm.

00:13:17.582 --> 00:13:18.260
[LAUGH]

00:13:18.260 --> 00:13:20.380
&gt;&gt; Versus someone else was like, oh I can't stand

00:13:20.380 --> 00:13:22.440
them and then you know, whatever else happens from there on.

00:13:22.440 --> 00:13:23.440
&gt;&gt;

00:13:22.440 --> 00:13:22.940
[LAUGH]

00:13:22.940 --> 00:13:29.190
&gt;&gt; So I don't, it, at that point it depends on what the attitude is.

00:13:29.190 --> 00:13:29.790
&gt;&gt; Mm hmm

00:13:29.790 --> 00:13:31.930
&gt;&gt; Of the person, or of the people in

00:13:31.930 --> 00:13:36.570
a certain area towards others at that point in time.

00:13:36.570 --> 00:13:38.840
&gt;&gt; Sure, and actually that's really interesting that you

00:13:38.840 --> 00:13:40.100
say it like that, I mean when you moved to

00:13:40.100 --> 00:13:43.190
San Francisco, and you see, you know? Okay, now

00:13:43.190 --> 00:13:48.290
your part of a, a minority group and, Do people,

00:13:48.290 --> 00:13:53.280
you know, use skin color in the same way, as far as signifiers, in, in the San

00:13:53.280 --> 00:13:55.050
Francisco area? I mean, you know? In the

00:13:55.050 --> 00:13:56.510
same way that you say, I mean. Where you're

00:13:56.510 --> 00:13:57.760
from, you can use it as, like, an

